CHANGES

Here lies all of the changes made during the version upgrade from 0.77 to 0.80A

New Help System Backend
Help Files Updated
Now displays non-hidden closed and locked doors to non-perceiving/projecting chars
Knock command
Weather changing re-enabled
Weather/Time specific messages when leaving a building
New Newbie Guild and Chargen Process
Player death messages changed
Critical Combat bug affecting dodge fixed (Was using TN equal to power of the weapon, not 4)
Hunger, Thirst, Drunk Messages Changed

